Exam Tips:
Understand the concepts deeply and don’t just memorize tools and techniques.

Get hands-on experience using tools like Kali Linux to perform real-world tests.

Time management: During the exam, keep an eye on the time and make sure you attempt all questions.

The exam format is 125 multiple-choice questions, and you’ll have 4 hours to complete it.
Thats mean = <2 mins per questions

Review the official EC-Council Study Guide and take practice exams to identify weak areas.
